  "plan": "1) Install lsof for identifying the process using port 5901. 2) Find the PID listening on 5901 and kill it so QEMU can bind to VNC :1. 3) Start QEMU in the background with the ISO, the qcow2 disk, and the floppy image; explicitly set the floppy format to raw. 4) Verify QEMU is running, that port 5901 is listening, and check the QEMU log for errors.",
